Good news!

186
00:10:36,760 --> 00:10:39,800
Mr. Wen Junior
has become the top scholar.

187
00:10:40,000 --> 00:10:41,240
Mr. Wen Junior is back?

188
00:10:41,240 --> 00:10:42,040
Where is he?

189
00:10:42,320 --> 00:10:44,240
Perhaps too many people
are watching him.

190
00:10:44,240 --> 00:10:45,040
It delayed him.

191
00:10:46,360 --> 00:10:47,280
Good news!

192
