has become the top scholar.

195
00:10:56,680 --> 00:10:57,600
Congratulations, Madam.

196
00:10:57,800 --> 00:10:59,560
Mr. Wen Junior
has become the top scholar.

197
00:10:59,840 --> 00:11:00,680
Where is Su?

198
00:11:00,840 --> 00:11:02,160
Mr. Wen has gone to see him.

199
00:11:03,480 --> 00:11:06,000
Fortunately,
Su didn't work hard in vain.

200
00:11:07,360 --> 00:11:08,160
Congrats, Mr. Wen.

201
00:11:08,160 --> 00:11:09,080
Congrats, Mr. Wen.

202
00:11:09,080 --> 00:11:11,280
Congrats to Mr. Wen Junior for becoming
the top scholar.

203
00:11:11,280 --> 00:11:12,040
Thank you.

204
00:11:12,360 --> 00:11:13,960
Today is a great day.

205
00:11:13,960 --> 00:11:15,720
I will grant you a day off.

206
00:11:16,120 --> 00:11:16,960
- Thank you.
- Thank you.

207
00:11:16,960 --> 00:11:17,800
You may go.

208
00:11:40,960 --> 00:11:42,160
Greetings, Captain.

209
00:11:42,560 --> 00:11:43,440
What brings you here?

210
00:11:43,440 --> 00:11:44,440
The whole Wen family,

211
00:11:44,440 --> 00:11:46,600
except for married daughters
and those under 15,

212
00:11:47,080 --> 00:11:48,760
is all implicated and imprisoned.

213
00:11:50,560 --> 00:11:51,720
Confiscate property as well.

214
00:11:59,560 --> 00:12:00,520
Captain.

215
00:12:00,520 --> 00:12:01,680
Why is this?

216
00:12:02,040 --> 00:12:03,600
I have been diligent all my life.

217
00:12:03,600 --> 00:12:06,000
For Bianyang Prefecture,
I have never committed any crime.

218
00:12:06,120 --> 00:12:07,904
Minister Song offended His Majesty

219
00:12:08,000 --> 00:12:09,240
and got punished for his words.

220
00:12:09,240 --> 00:12:11,080
You've corresponded with him for years.

221
00:12:11,080 --> 00:12:12,400
You may be his accomplice.

222
00:12:13,000 --> 00:12:13,880
Mr. Wen.

223
00:12:13,880 --> 00:12:15,280
It's His Majesty's order.

224
00:12:15,760 --> 00:12:17,520
I am just following it.

225
00:12:17,960 --> 00:12:19,000
You'll have to excuse me.

226
00:12:22,200 --> 00:12:23,000
Proceed!

227
00:12:23,800 --> 00:12:25,120
Madam, hurry.

228
00:12:30,840 --> 00:12:31,480
Wait.

229
00:12:31,800 --> 00:12:33,320
Sir, I'm wronged.

230
00:12:33,840 --> 00:12:35,120
It's a misunderstanding.

231
00:12:35,120 --> 00:12:36,360
It's a misunderstanding.

232
00:12:37,240 --> 00:12:38,000
Madam.

233
00:12:41,280 --> 00:12:42,920
Take your money and indentures

234
00:12:43,200 --> 00:12:44,080
and leave.

235
00:12:44,320 --> 00:12:45,640
Don't get implicated.

236
00:12:46,040 --> 00:12:46,720
Leave!

237
00:12:46,720 --> 00:12:47,400
We won't leave.

238
00:12:47,640 --> 00:12:48,440
You take them away.

239
00:12:48,440 --> 00:12:49,680
Let's go right away.

240
00:12:49,680 --> 00:12:50,160
Madam.

241
00:12:50,160 --> 00:12:50,960
Madam, take care.

242
00:12:52,120 --> 00:12:52,720
Baoyin.

243
00:12:53,040 --> 00:12:54,040
Why haven't you left yet?

244
00:12:54,960 --> 00:12:55,440
Madam.

245
00:12:55,800 --> 00:12:56,720
What about Qiongniang?

246
00:12:56,880 --> 00:12:58,000
I can take care of her.

247
00:13:00,600 --> 00:13:01,440
Good girl.

248
00:13:02,680 --> 00:13:04,000
Qiongniang is lucky to have you.

249
00:13:07,280 --> 00:13:09,040
I still have some money left.

250
00:13:09,040 --> 00:13:09,800
You take it.

251
00:13:10,240 --> 00:13:10,880
Take Qiongniang

252
00:13:11,160 --> 00:13:12,720
to Su Mansion to find her sister.

253
00:13:12,720 --> 00:13:14,640
Mother, I don't want to leave.

254
00:13:14,640 --> 00:13:16,240
I don't want to leave you.

255
00:13:16,320 --> 00:13:18,280
I want to be with you and father.

256
00:13:18,280 --> 00:13:19,440
Be good.

257
00:13:19,760 --> 00:13:21,360
You still have many days to live.

258
00:13:21,960 --> 00:13:24,160
Mother.

259
00:13:24,576 --> 00:13:25,520
Take care of yourself.

260
00:13:25,720 --> 00:13:27,000
You must survive

261
00:13:27,320 --> 00:13:28,240
and live well.

262
00:13:29,360 --> 00:13:30,240
Leave quickly!

263
00:13:31,800 --> 00:13:32,800
Take her away.

264
00:13:34,080 --> 00:13:35,120
Madam, don't worry.

265
00:13:35,240 --> 00:13:36,400
I will send her there.

266
00:13:36,600 --> 00:13:38,280
I will protect her with my life.

267
00:13:38,920 --> 00:13:39,440
Leave!

268
00:13:39,440 --> 00:13:41,240
Mother, I'm not leaving.

269
00:13:41,240 --> 00:13:42,920
Let me stay.

270
00:13:44,320 --> 00:13:45,440
I don't want to leave.

271
00:13:45,440 --> 00:13:46,200
Qiongniang.

272
00:13:47,400 --> 00:13:49,120
I'm not leaving.

273
00:13:52,600 --> 00:13:54,440
Qiongniang, let's go quickly.

274
00:13:54,880 --> 00:13:56,560
Hurry up.

275
00:13:57,000 --> 00:13:57,720
Come on.

276
00:13:58,440 --> 00:14:00,080
I don't want to leave.

277
00:14:01,240 --> 00:14:02,000
Go!

278
00:14:05,760 --> 00:14:07,480
Let go of me.

279
00:14:07,920 --> 00:14:09,160
I want to stay with my mother.

280
00:14:09,160 --> 00:14:10,360
Go!

281
00:14:10,360 --> 00:14:12,160
Mother.

282
00:14:13,480 --> 00:14:14,320
(You must survive)

283
00:14:14,800 --> 00:14:16,280
(and live well.)

284
00:14:19,014 --> 00:14:24,710
♪In a dreamlike haze,
our joys and sorrows blend♪

285
00:14:24,710 --> 00:14:28,454
♪When the glory's gone,
this love will never end♪

286
00:14:30,022 --> 00:14:35,270
